(10, 1, '2018-06-13 18:31:37', '2018-06-13 18:31:37', '<div class=\"inner_left\">\r\n<div class=\"casestudy_detail service-div\">\r\n<h2 class=\"quotes mtop50\" align=\"center\">Covering the full spectrum of web centric interactions.\r\nRooted in individual business priorities.</h2>\r\nWhether a first-time web entrepreneur or a large corporate, we have the creativity, experience and resources to put the Web to work for you. With a range of skills that covers all aspects of web-based interactions rooted in your business priorities - ranging from strategic consulting to delivery, all in-house.\r\n\r\n<b>The services include, but are not limited by, the following:</b>\r\n<div class=\"clients\">\r\n<dl>\r\n 	<dt><img title=\"E-commerce applications\" src=\"http://www.whatarage.com/images/ecommerce-applications.jpg\" alt=\"E-commerce applications\" /></dt>\r\n 	<dd>\r\n<h2>E-COMMERCE APPLICATIONS</h2>\r\nE-commerce sites can vary dramatically in complexity depending on the extent of functionality, automation, and analytical capability required by the web-marketer. Over the years, we have developed commerce and transactional solutions to meet a wide variety of client requirements.\r\n\r\nREAD MORE</dd>\r\n</dl>\r\n<dl>\r\n 	<dt><img title=\"Website Design and Development\" src=\"http://www.whatarage.com/images/online-marketing.jpg\" alt=\"Website Design and Development\" /></dt>\r\n 	<dd>\r\n<h2>WEBSITE DESIGN AND DEVELOPMENT</h2>\r\nSince we incorporated in 1996, we have delivered for a diverse range of clients - from start-ups with dreams to the hard-nosed Fortune 10 corporations in all parts of the world.\r\n\r\nREAD MORE</dd>\r\n</dl>\r\n<dl>\r\n 	<dt><img title=\"Workflow Application\" src=\"http://www.whatarage.com/images/online-workflow-applications.jpg\" alt=\"Workflow Application\" /></dt>\r\n 	<dd>\r\n<h2>ONLINE WORKFLOW APPLICATIONS</h2>\r\nMany of our clients operate from multiple geographical locations and interact with partners and vendors around the globe. 